          </ul></div><div id="posts"><article class="post type-text" id="42603252487"><aside class="metadata not-custom-page"><a class="timestamp" href="lesson-134-the-verb-lagnaa-part-1">February 8th, 2013</a><!--  
                               <a class="note-count" href="http://www.learning-hindi.com/post/42603252487/lesson-134-the-verb-लगन-lagnaa-part-1#notes">18 notes</a> --><a class="comment-count" href="lesson-134-the-verb-lagnaa-part-1#disqus_thread"></a><script type="text/javascript">
